title: Week 1 Liquidity Mining Proposal
body:
This marks the beginning of liquidity mining on Balancer v2. The Ballers propose allocating 2500 BAL to each of the following pools for the week starting Monday, May 24th at 00:00 UTC:

BAL/WETH 80/20 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0x5c6ee304399dbdb9c8ef030ab642b10820db8f56000200000000000000000014

WETH/DAI 60/40 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0x0b09dea16768f0799065c475be02919503cb2a3500020000000000000000001a

WBTC/WETH 50/50 https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0xa6f548df93de924d73be7d25dc02554c6bd66db500020000000000000000000e

The pull request reflecting these changes can be found here: https://github.com/balancer-labs/frontend-v2/pull/375
